---
description: Project layering and ownership
alwaysApply: false
---

- Explain project layering: Web (Next.js admin), API (Fastify), Domain (shared types and policy), future infra.
- Keep UI, API, domain, and infra concerns separated.
- No shortcut imports across forbidden boundaries (e.g. web must not import from api; domain must not depend on web or server runtimes).
- Allowed ownership by folder:
  - **agent-control-tower/apps/web/** — frontend only; no direct server or domain implementation.
  - **agent-control-tower/apps/api/** — HTTP boundary and orchestration only; business logic in domain.
  - **agent-control-tower/packages/domain/** — shared types and pure policy/domain logic; no framework leakage.
